HEADWORD: Bewitchery
<hw>Be*witch"er*y</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The power of
bewitching or fascinating; bewitchment; charm; fascination.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>There is a certain <qex>bewitchery</qex> or fascination in
words.</q> <rj><qau>South.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Bewitching</ent>⟦br⟧
